Errol Ginsberg's Biography




			Mr. Ginsberg has been a director of the Company since May 1997, and became the Chairman of our Board of Directors (the "Board") in January 2008. Mr. Ginsberg served as the Company's President from May 1997 until September 2007 and as the Company's Chief Executive Officer from September 2000 until March 2008. In March 2008, Mr. Ginsberg became our Chief Innovation Officer. He held the additional position of Acting Chief Executive Officer from October 2013 until September 2014. Mr. Ginsberg has also served on the boards of directors of several privately held technology companies.
		
Source: Ixia on 04/17/2017
		
	

 






